description: Returns a list of transit gateway policy table entries.

parameters.name: TransitGatewayPolicyTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the transit gateway policy table.

parameters.name: Filters
parameters.description: The filters associated with the transit gateway policy table. (dict) --- A filter name and value pair that is used to return a more specific list of results from a describe operation. Filters can be used to match a set of resources by specific criteria, such as tags, attributes, or IDs. If you specify multiple filters, the filters are joined with an AND, and the request returns only results that match all of the specified filters. For more information, see List and filter using the CLI and API in the Amazon EC2 User Guide. Name (string) --- The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive. Values (list) --- The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values. (string) ---

nested_params.name: Name
nested_params.description: The name of the filter. Filter names are case-sensitive.

nested_params.name: Values
nested_params.description: The filter values. Filter values are case-sensitive. If you specify multiple values for a filter, the values are joined with an OR, and the request returns all results that match any of the specified values.

nested_items.name: TransitGatewayPolicyTableEntries
nested_items.description: The entries for the transit gateway policy table.

nested_items.name: PolicyRuleNumber
nested_items.description: The rule number for the transit gateway policy table entry.

nested_items.name: PolicyRule
nested_items.description: The policy rule associated with the transit gateway policy table.

nested_items.name: SourceCidrBlock
nested_items.description: The source CIDR block for the transit gateway policy rule.

nested_items.name: SourcePortRange
nested_items.description: The port range for the transit gateway policy rule. Currently this is set to * (all).

nested_items.name: DestinationCidrBlock
nested_items.description: The destination CIDR block for the transit gateway policy rule.

nested_items.name: DestinationPortRange
nested_items.description: The port range for the transit gateway policy rule. Currently this is set to * (all).

nested_items.name: Protocol
nested_items.description: The protocol used by the transit gateway policy rule.

nested_items.name: MetaDataKey
nested_items.description: The key name for the transit gateway policy rule meta data tag.

nested_items.name: MetaDataValue
nested_items.description: The value of the key for the transit gateway policy rule meta data tag.

nested_items.name: TargetRouteTableId
nested_items.description: The ID of the target route table.
